msgctxt "Diary00"
msgid ""
"<1.ra>On this desolate plateau, the only\n"
"pleasure that brings me comfort\n"
"is cooking.\n"
"<2.ra>And today, I outdid myself! Truly,\n"
"I created the perfect dish. I call it...\n"
"spicy meat and seafood fry."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
#. 2: raw
#. 3: set_colour (blue)
#. 4: reset_colour
#. 5: choice
msgctxt "Diary01"
msgid ""
"<1.ra>This recipe not only restores health,\n"
"but it also keeps me warm, even when\n"
"traveling in the snowy mountains.\n"
"<2.ra>With this dish on my side, I no longer\n"
"have need of that itchy <3.se_co>warm doublet<4.re_co>.<5.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
#. 2: raw
#. 3: raw
#. 4: choice
msgctxt "Diary02"
msgid ""
"<1.ra>I do not know how I allowed this to\n"
"happen, but it seems I forgot to\n"
"write down a very important recipe.\n"
"<2.ra>I know it contained raw meat and\n"
"spicy pepper. However...\n"
"\n"
"<3.ra>I simply cannot remember what else\n"
"I used! My age is catching up to me.<4.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
#. 2: raw
#. 3: set_colour (blue)
#. 4: reset_colour
#. 5: raw
#. 6: raw
msgctxt "Diary03"
msgid ""
"<1.ra>Sadly, on this lonely plateau, I have only\n"
"my own knowledge and memory to\n"
"rely on. Still...\n"
"<2.ra>If I did find someone who knew the\n"
"missing ingredient, I would happily\n"
"reward them with my <3.se_co>warm doublet<4.re_co>.\n"
"<5.ra>However, it seems unlikely that such a\n"
"miraculous wish will ever be fulfilled.<6.ra>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
#. 2: raw
#. 3: set_colour (blue)
#. 4: reset_colour
#. 5: choice
msgctxt "Diary04"
msgid ""
"<1.ra>To my surprise and delight, I did happen\n"
"upon someone who was able to re-create\n"
"my spicy meat and seafood fry.\n"
"<2.ra>I gave him my <3.se_co>warm doublet<4.re_co>, and I was\n"
"happy to do so. He is a fine young man\n"
"with great potential, that one.<5.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
#. 2: raw
#. 3: choice
msgctxt "Diary05"
msgid ""
"<1.ra>Ah, and I will now write down this\n"
"perfect recipe so that I will never\n"
"forget it.\n"
"<2.ra>Place some raw meat, spicy pepper,\n"
"and hyrule bass in a pot, and then\n"
"turn up the heat. Voil√†!<3.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
#. 2: raw
#. 3: set_colour (blue)
#. 4: reset_colour
#. 5: raw
msgctxt "Diary06"
msgid ""
"<1.ra>Eating this dish allows you to walk the\n"
"snowy mountains with ease, though I did\n"
"forget there's a time limit on the effect.\n"
"<2.ra>It is too bad I already gave away that\n"
"<3.se_co>warm doublet<4.re_co>, which keeps you warm\n"
"no matter how long you wear it.<5.ra>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
#. 2: raw
#. 3: raw
#. 4: choice
msgctxt "Diary07"
msgid ""
"<1.ra>Link...\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"<2.ra>Bit by bit, you may come to realize who\n"
"I am. I am sorry for not revealing my\n"
"true identity to you sooner.\n"
"<3.ra>The truth is, after you awoke from your\n"
"long Slumber of Restoration, I did not\n"
"know how to tell you all there was to say.<4.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
#. 2: raw
#. 3: raw
#. 4: raw
#. 5: raw
#. 6: raw
msgctxt "Diary08a"
msgid ""
"<1.ra>Perhaps deceiving you was not the right\n"
"thing to do. Still...you must admit I put\n"
"on a great performance!\n"
"<2.ra>But all joking aside...what I ask of you\n"
"is of the utmost importance, dear hero.\n"
"\n"
"<3.ra>I implore you, with all my heart...\n"
"defeat Calamity Ganon and save\n"
"my precious daughter, Zelda.\n"
"<4.ra>I understand this is no simple task I am\n"
"asking of you, but I know beyond a\n"
"shadow of a doubt that you can do it.\n"
"<5.ra>I do not doubt it for a moment. I see\n"
"courage in your eyes, just as I did\n"
"100 years ago. I believe in you, Link.<6.ra>"
msgstr ""

