msgctxt "Diary09"
msgid ""
"<1.ra>Ah, yes, one more thing. I have left the\n"
"<2.se_co>warm doublet <3.re_co>here as a gift of sorts.\n"
"I'm sure it will be useful on your journey.\n"
"<4.ra>You can also weather the cold with\n"
"cooking alone, but I caution against it.\n"
"There is no time for recklessness.\n"
"<5.ra>We are all counting on you.<6.ra>"
msgstr ""

